{"tid":1964894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地就可食用陸上動物名單徵求意見　狗隻不列入名單","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T06:52:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e32ab00c29e0b04547f51106c9f3263903268339","tid":1964894,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"國家農業農村部就法例下可食用陸上動物名單徵求意見，名單上列出31種動物，包括雞、鴨、鵝、豬、牛、羊等傳統禽畜，以及鹿、駝鳥和銀狐等特種禽畜，但並無狗隻。<br />\n<br />\n農業農村部在徵求意見稿的說明中回應說，隨著人類文明進步和公眾對動物保護的關注及偏愛，狗已從傳統家畜變為伴侶動物，國際上普遍不視為禽畜，所以不適宜列入禽畜管理名單。<br />\n<br />\n武漢冠狀病毒疫情發生後，全國人大常委會早前通過有關革除濫食野生動物陋習的決定，表明全面禁止食用有重要生態、科學、社會價值的陸上野生動物。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519749-20200409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519749-20200409.htm&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b368fed6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519749-20200409.htm&h=4d2fab1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519749-20200409.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6f2645d2021c2808ae46d1448a5f946ce2187671","tid":1964894,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"銀狐？"},{"pid":"003978b4fff0722cc265abb1a7413d2c7f581ee6","tid":1964894,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"銀狐都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3e6ff9f20ae530b21f12f0da90e7f99bdb0952","tid":1964894,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"中國夠禁黃色場面啦"},{"pid":"176fdd3641eeb4e66878eb2a1f99e3ad6a05f9c6","tid":1964894,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"即係陸上動物名單啦"},{"pid":"d677302dd695a640ca3f7a01622b17a00f2d9019","tid":1964894,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"冇得食狗肉，又準備微博暴動"},{"pid":"41b49c8e52d20dd82ecebd016c5977dc2c3a51b3","tid":1964894,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f2645d2021c2808ae46d1448a5f946ce2187671","tid":1964894,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"銀狐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2c/Silberfuchs_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F2c%2FSilberfuchs_06.jpg&h=d3ce24fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91115767470cc87cac19a5e488f5df250f7914dc","tid":1964894,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"其實咩都得<br />\n最主要係專業、衛生同法治<br />\n我唔見得限咗31就無事<br />\n垃圾國家終歸會出事"},{"pid":"460275e455e8e12d25ff6197bbd45dcbd068e3f9","tid":1964894,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線國度"},{"pid":"d6447355420232c4930e9e766968e3bc2960a0bc","tid":1964894,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"支那國人都食得喇<br />\n過去每個朝代大飢荒時都會人食人"},{"pid":"a3079086bc8dec17f1ec948741e87715709fa5fc","tid":1964894,"uid":201036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32ab00c29e0b04547f51106c9f3263903268339","tid":1964894,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"國家農業農村部就法例下可食用陸上動物名單徵求意見，名單上列出31種動物，包括雞、鴨、鵝、豬、牛、羊等傳統禽畜，以及鹿、駝鳥和銀狐等特種禽畜，但並無狗隻。<br />\n<br />\n農業農村部在徵求意見稿的說明中回應說，隨著人類文明進步和公眾對動物保護的關注及偏愛，狗已從傳統家畜變為伴侶動物，國際上普遍不視為禽畜，所以不適宜列入禽畜管理名單。<br />\n<br />\n武漢冠狀病毒疫情發生後，全國人大常委會早前通過有關革除濫食野生動物陋習的決定，表明全面禁止食用有重要生態、科學、社會價值的陸上野生動物。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519749-20200409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk